Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: President Bush II has never been busier, 2002
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00sxbyr
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 6 Sep 2002
Alistair Cooke reflects on President George Bush's recent holiday and considers the workload of "the most powerful man in the world" with reference to the Iraq crisis.